<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <title>Job Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .job-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background-color: #e5f1ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .job-info {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .apply-btn {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .apply-btn:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
            }

        .job-details-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .job-description {
            flex: 3;
        }

        .more-jobs-container {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .job-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .job-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .location-badge {
            background-color: #e0ecff;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .level-badge {
            background-color: #ffe0e0;
            color: #d9534f;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="job-header" style="min-height:200px;">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="~/images/slack.png" class="logo">
            </div>
            <div class="job-info">
                <h2>Full Stack Developer</h2>
                <p>
                    <i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Slack &nbsp;
                    <span class="job-meta">
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/684/684809.png" alt="Location" width="16" style="margin-right: 4px; margin-left: 10px;"> California
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/847/847969.png" alt="Level" width="16" style="margin-right: 4px; margin-left: 15px;"> Senior Level
                    </span>
                    <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave" style="margin-left: 15px;"></i> CTC: 80k
                </p>


            </div>
            <div>
                <button class="apply-btn">Apply now</button>
                <p class="text-muted">Posted 25 mins ago</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="job-details-container">
            <div class="job-description">
                <div class="job-card">
                    <h3>Job Description</h3>
                    <p>
                        We are looking for a talented Full Stack Developer to join our dynamic and innovative team. The ideal candidate should
                        be passionate about building scalable web applications and working across the full technology stack, from front-end 
                        interfaces to back-end databases and server management</br>
                        </br>

                        You will work closely with cross-functional teams to design, develop, and deploy new features, ensuring optimal
                        performance, responsiveness, and security. If you excel in fast-paced environments, have a keen eye for detail, and enjoy tackling complex technical challenges, we’d love to connect with you!.
                    </p>
                    <h4>Key Responsibilities</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Develop, test, and deploy dynamic web applications using the latest front-end and back-end technologies. </li>
                        <li> Create intuitive user interfaces with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript frameworks like React, Angular, or Vue.js.</li>
                        <li>Develop and manage APIs, server-side logic, and databases using technologies such as Node.js, Ruby, or Java.</li>
                        <li>Optimize and maintain SQL and NoSQL databases for scalability and reliability.</li>
                        <li>Implement automated testing (unit, integration, and end-to-end) to ensure software quality.</li>
                        <li>Collaborate with designers, product managers, and engineers to translate requirements into functional features..</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Skills Required</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Proficiency in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, with experience in frameworks like React, Angular, or Vue.js.
                        </li>
                        <li>Hands-on experience with server-side languages such as Node.js, Python, Ruby, or Java.</li>
                        <li>Strong understanding of relational (MySQL, PostgreSQL) and non-relational (MongoDB) databases.L</li>
                        <li>Experience with Git for version control and collaborative development.</li>
                        <li>Excellent communication and teamwork skills to work effectively in a collaborative environment.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <button class="apply-btn">Apply Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="more-jobs-container">
                <h4>More jobs from Slack</h4>
                <div class="job-card">
                    <img src="~/images/slack.png" class="logo">
                    <h4>Frontend Developer</h4>
                    <span class="job-badge location-badge">California</span>
                    <span class="job-badge level-badge">Senior Level</span>
                    <p>You will be responsible for frontend and backend development tasks...</p>
                    <div class="button-group">
                        <button class="apply-btn">Apply Now</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Learn More</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="job-card">
                    <img src="~/images/slack.png" class="logo">
                    <h4>Backend Developer</h4>
                    <span class="job-badge location-badge">California</span>
                    <span class="job-badge level-badge">Senior Level</span>
                    <p>You will be responsible for backend development tasks...</p>
                    <div class="button-group">
                        <button class="apply-btn">Apply Now</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Learn More</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="job-card">
                    <img src="~/images/slack.png" class="logo">
                    <h4>Website Developer</h4>
                    <span class="job-badge location-badge">California</span>
                    <span class="job-badge level-badge">Senior Level</span>
                    <p>You will be responsible for website developer tasks...</p>
                    <div class="button-group">
                        <button class="apply-btn">Apply Now</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Learn More</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
